---
title: "Publishing"
format: 
  html: 
    highlight-style: dracula
---

To make the blog or website into an actual website, use quarto publish (you will need to create an account)

-   In the terminal, type `quarto publish quarto-pub`

-   It will then ask you to authorise your account, and pick a site name

-   The URL will be https://your_account_name.quarto.pub/site_name

-   example: https://ks745.quarto.pub/r-guide
